    properties:
      locator: "High Sparrow"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Male, unknown real name. Titles: Septon, High Septon, Father of the Faithful, His High Holiness, Shepherd of the Faithful, Voice of the Seven on Earth. Allegiance: Faith of the Seven, Sparrows, Faith Militant. Appears in AFFC and ADWD."
